generateTimetableCommands

public java.util.List<java.lang.String> generateTimetableCommands(FHTDevice device,
                                                                  java.util.List<java.lang.String> commandParts)
Generates the actual timetable commands from some given command parts. A FHT command may contain up to 8 command parts. As FHT command evaluation is lazy, this should be used excessively.

Parameters:
device - concerned device
commandParts - some parts of the future commands. A part is like "mon-from1 08:00".
Returns:
list of FHT commands like "set device_name mon-from1 08:00 mon-from2 17:00"
